OL,3,CMan with disabilities faces #3,300
OL,4,Cbill to be able to drive
OL,6,FA man with disabilities from Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas spoken about the financial
OL,8,Fdifficulties people like him face when
OL,9,Ftrying to drive.
OL,11,FDavid Walsh is a double-leg amputee
OL,12,Fand needs his car to be specially
OL,13,Fmodified with levers to control
OL,14,Findicator lights, the horn,
OL,15,Facceleration and braking.
OL,17,FHe has been told it will cost #2,860
OL,18,Fas specialist mechanics have to fly
OL,19,Fover from the UK and the work will
OL,20,Ftake a couple of days.
