OL,3,CMan with disabilities faces #3,300
OL,4,Cbill to be able to drive
OL,6,FDavid then needs to take a specialist
OL,7,Fdriving test in the adapted car which
OL,8,Fwill set him back another #500.
OL,10,FWith no grants available to cover at
OL,11,Fleast part of the cost, David says it
OL,12,Fis restricting his independence.
OL,14,FHe explains: "You know you are capable
OL,15,Fof doing these things but you don't
OL,16,Fhave the ability to do it because you
OL,17,Fare not getting any help.
OL,19,F"There are plenty of people on the
OL,20,Fisland who have amputations and they
OL,21,Fneed help, but where do they get it?"
