OL,3,CMan with disabilities faces #3,300
OL,4,Cbill to be able to drive
OL,6,FA Jersey charity does offer cheaper
OL,7,Fexaminations but it involves
OL,8,Ftravelling - something not everyone
OL,9,Fcan do.
OL,11,FTerry Dowinton used to run a Guernsey
OL,12,Fequivalent to help prospective drivers
OL,13,Flike David but he stopped after his
OL,14,Fwife fell ill.
OL,16,FHe says: "It saddens me and worries me
OL,17,Fas if I had to have an assessment
OL,18,Fagain then I wouldn't be able to
OL,19,Ftravel either.
