OL,3,CMan with disabilities faces #3,300
OL,4,Cbill to be able to drive
OL,6,F"I would lose my independence. I look
OL,7,Fafter myself and live on my own so the
OL,8,FStates may have to look after me
OL,9,Finstead."
OL,11,FIn response, the Lead Officer for
OL,12,FTraffic and Highway Services, Colin Le
OL,13,FPage, says: "Since the closure of
OL,14,FGuernsey Driveability last year, who
OL,15,Fpreviously carried out these
OL,16,Fspecialist assessments, we've been
OL,17,Fexploring the options to provide these
OL,18,Fservices locally.
