OL,4,Cbill to be able to drive
OL,6,F"A new scheme has been implemented for
OL,7,Fcases where a driver's cognitive
OL,8,Fability needs to be assessed.
OL,10,F"However, we are still exploring
OL,11,Fwhether or not we can provide
OL,12,Fassessment services for those
OL,13,Frequiring vehicle modifications and,
OL,14,Fif so, who can assess these locally
OL,15,Fand for what type of modifications."
